30</em> ). </p><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /><div class="wp-block-image  has-alignleft" style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"><figure class="alignleft size-large is-resized"> <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/21798/9781324005087" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/103123_reviews_cover_bears.jpg?resize=149%2C225&#038;ssl=1" alt="עטיפת הספרים &quot;שמונה דובים&quot;" class="wp-image-3133714" width="149" height="225" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/103123_reviews_cover_bears.jpg?resize=298%2C450&amp;ssl=1 298w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/103123_reviews_cover_bears.jpg?resize=254%2C383&amp;ssl=1 254w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/103123_reviews_cover_bears.jpg?resize=123%2C186&amp;ssl=1 123w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/103123_reviews_cover_bears.jpg?resize=384%2C580&amp;ssl=1 384w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/103123_reviews_cover_bears.jpg?resize=514%2C776&amp;ssl=1 514w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/103123_reviews_cover_bears.jpg?w=680&amp;ssl=1 680w" sizes="(max-width: 149px) 100vw, 149px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></figure></div><p style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"> <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/21798/9781324005087" target="_blank" rel="noopener">שמונה דובים</a><br> <em>גלוריה דיקי</em><br> <em>WW Norton &amp; Co., 30 דולר</em></p><p style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"> כתב נוסע בשלוש יבשות <a href="https://www.sciencenews.org/article/eight-bears-book-conservation">לפגוש את שמונה מינים הדובים שנותרו בעולם</a> , חולק סיפורי מדע, פולקלור ושימור לאורך הדרך ( <em>SN: 7/15/23 &amp; 7/29/23, עמ &#39;33</em> ). </p><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /><div class="wp-block-image  has-align